<p>WineConf 2005 will be held in Stuttgart April 30th and May 1st, 2005.  
You should plan on arriving on April 29th unless you can arrive very early
on Saturday.  We'll probably organize an informal dinner on Friday night.
At this point, much remains to done and the number of people attending 
will likely determine the agenda.</p>

<p>You may also be interested in a Samba conference nearby following
WineConf.   
<a href="http://www.sambaxp.org/">SambaXP</a> will be held in G&ouml;ttingen,
Germany on May 2-3.  </p>


